import { Col, Card, Container, Image } from "react-bootstrap";
function Ratings (props) {
    return (
        <Container fluid className="m-2">
        <Col className="d-flex justify-content-center">
        <Card className="text-center d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"
        style={{ width: '200px', height: '200px' }}>
      <Card.Header>{props.header}</Card.Header>
      <Card.Title>{props.title}</Card.Title>
      <Image className="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"
      roundedCircle variant="top"
      src={props.image} height={100} width={100}/>
      <Card.Body>
        <Card.Title>{props.title}</Card.Title>
        <Card.Text>
          {props.text}
        </Card.Text>
      </Card.Body>
    </Card>
    </Col>
    </Container>
    )

}

export default Ratings;
